    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/a39c97ca92661d04b83c24abf71c6cb3.poster.avif?t=1727881231\" width=500 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/a39c97ca92661d04b83c24abf71c6cb3.webm?t=1727881231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/a39c97ca92661d04b83c24abf71c6cb3.mp4?t=1727881231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><u>滚动并征服！！</u></strong><br>《滚动足球运动员》是一款充满戏仿元素的足球运动员滚动挑战各种运动项目的动作游戏！！清除设置在城市不同地方的五个阶段，包括家、公园、仓库等！！<br><br><strong><i>欢迎视频分享</i></strong><br>非常欢迎视频发布和分享！！这款游戏是由拥有五万名订阅者的YouTube游戏主播“Shinise”制作的运动挑战游戏！！理解缩略图的重要性，我们加入了使用鼠标滚轮缩放等功能，让主播们感到满意！！让我们一起制作许多优秀的缩略图吧！！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/8cec080b5102f20ce8029bc0d6c29cef.poster.avif?t=1727881231\" width=500 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/8cec080b5102f20ce8029bc0d6c29cef.webm?t=1727881231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/8cec080b5102f20ce8029bc0d6c29cef.mp4?t=1727881231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>难度</i></strong><br>有难度选择功能！根据自己的喜好享受游戏吧！<br><br><strong><i>游戏时间</i></strong><br>30分钟到120分钟<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/706ce76ba8273effee9b0e63bd1eff65.poster.avif?t=1727881231\" width=500 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/706ce76ba8273effee9b0e63bd1eff65.webm?t=1727881231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/706ce76ba8273effee9b0e63bd1eff65.mp4?t=1727881231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><u>视频分享指南</u></strong><br>个人和企业无需许可即可分享视频，但请查看并遵守以下指南：<br><br>在视频或直播的标题中包含游戏名称。<br>可选，但如果能在简介中包含Steam页面的链接，我们将不胜感激。<br>仅允许通过视频分享网站提供的功能进行货币化。<br>允许有偿直播，例如YouTube会员限定直播。<br>对因分享此游戏视频而造成的任何损害，我们概不负责。<br>本指南内容如有变更，恕不另行通知。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/e7fd6a8bbd081d6022aa2f7446ad1ac6.poster.avif?t=1727881231\" width=500 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/e7fd6a8bbd081d6022aa2f7446ad1ac6.webm?t=1727881231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125650/extras/e7fd6a8bbd081d6022aa2f7446ad1ac6.mp4?t=1727881231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>操作方法</i></strong><br>对于键盘，使用WASD键移动，空格键跳跃。对于游戏手柄，使用摇杆移动角色，并使用相应的按钮跳跃。足球运动员的形状不均匀，所以在滚动时要预测动作，挑战运动项目。<br><br><strong><i>游戏说明</i></strong><br>游戏中有5个关卡，每个关卡的世界观都不同。在选择关卡后，可以选择有检查点的“简单模式”和没有检查点的“普通模式”，即使是运动游戏初学者也可以放心玩。每个关卡中有3个隐藏的足球，收集它们可以解锁新关卡。游戏内还会记录通关时间，所以请多次挑战，争取创造新记录！",
